141
00:15:51,990 --> 00:15:53,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Potret dia!</font>

142
00:15:53,320 --> 00:15:54,919
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sungguh membunuhnya? Katakan sesuatu.</font>

143
00:15:54,920 --> 00:15:56,489
