144
00:15:56,490 --> 00:15:58,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Minggirlah kalian semua!</font>

145
00:15:58,660 --> 00:16:00,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Katakan yang sebenarnya! Katakan sesuatu.</font>

146
00:16:01,260 --> 00:16:03,260
<font color=#FFFF00>("Park Eung Moo dicurigai membunuh empat orang wanita.")</font>

147
00:16:03,400 --> 00:16:05,900
